      h3(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/popover-js.html") Using JavaScript
      p We can also open and close Popover with JavaScript, for this we need to look at related App methods:
      p
        span.method myApp.popover(<span>popover</span>, <span>target</span>)</span> - open Popover around <strong>target</strong> element
      ul.method-parameters
        li
          span.parameter popover
          |  - <span class="parameter-type">HTMLElement</span> or <span class="parameter-type">string</span> (with CSS Selector) of Popover to open. Requred
        li
          span.parameter target
          |  - <span class="parameter-type">HTMLElement</span> or <span class="parameter-type">string</span> (with CSS Selector) of target element to set popover position around this element. Requred
        li.method-returns This method returns Popover's HTMLElement
      p
        span.method myApp.closeModal(<span>popover</span>)</span> - close Popover
      ul.method-parameters
        li
          span.parameter popover
          |  - <span class="parameter-type">HTMLElement</span> or <span class="parameter-type">string</span> (with CSS Selector). Optional. If not specified, any opened Popover will be closed
      h4 Popover position
      .important-note
        p When we open popover using JavaScript we need to pass <strong>target</strong> element to set popover around this target element.
      pre
        code
          | &lt;body&gt;
          |   ...
          |   &lt;div class="navbar"&gt;
          |     &lt;div class="navbar-inner"&gt;
          |       &lt;div class="left"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="link open-about"&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          |       &lt;div class="center"&gt;Popover&lt;/div&gt;
          |       &lt;div class="right"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="link open-about"&gt;Links&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          |     &lt;/div&gt;
          |   &lt;/div&gt;
          |   &lt;div class="page-content"&gt;
          |     &lt;div class="content-block"&gt;
          |       &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="open-about"&gt;Open About Popover&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          |       &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="open-links"&gt;Open Links Popover&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          |       &lt;p&gt;Praesent urna mi, sodales ac dolor vitae, dictum mattis sem. Mauris a dui faucibus, condimentum arcu quis, porta felis. Sed at metus arcu. Maecenas sodales tellus risus, id &lt;a href="#" class="open-about"&gt;About&lt;/a&gt; nibh iaculis quis. Suspendisse dignissim ante lobortis, molestie nibh id, pharetra risus. Proin blandit neque nec nibh scelerisque, eu vulputate ipsum malesuada. Phasellus sapien diam, fermentum eget ornare in, &lt;a href="#" class="open-links"&gt;Links&lt;/a&gt; rutrum vel justo. Integer accumsan posuere quam.&lt;/p&gt;
          |     &lt;/div&gt;
